    "description": "Jungle Lodges Karnataka Global Group is actively seeking a talented and motivated Hotel Manager to join our dynamic team in Meerut. This is an excellent opportunity for professionals who are passionate about making a real impact in a fast-growing organization.\n\nAbout Jungle Lodges Karnataka Global Group:\nJungle Lodges Karnataka Global Group is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Deliver exceptional guest experiences in line with brand standards\n• Monitor F&B service quality and maintain hygiene standards\n• Develop and maintain relationships with corporate clients\n• Assist in menu planning, costing, and food festival coordination\n• Coordinate housekeeping and maintenance for room readiness\n• Manage procurement of hotel supplies and control operating costs\n• Manage front office operations including check-in/check-out\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Ed / M.Ed from a recognized institution\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Hotel Management\n• Proficiency in OTA Management\n• Proficiency in Customer Relations\n• Proficiency in Revenue Management\n• Proficiency in Food Safety\n• Proficiency in Crisis Management\n• Proficiency in MICE\n• Proficiency in Yield Management\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Referral bonus program\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Flexible working hours\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Meerut, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Jungle Lodges Karnataka Global Group!",
